{"tid":2003121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港再出發]淺淡香港地產商係警魔反人類暴行的可恥參與","createTime":"2020-05-05T14:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T01:56:30.000Z","uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"98fc3c39ae78279a971253093ae19811bba3f079","tid":2003121,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:50:05.000Z","msg":"1 已經有人踢爆近期新紅GAY安裝大量閉路協助香港警魔鎖定女示威者<br />\n<br />\n2 大量五毛<br />\n相信大家都見就算係三流討論區,細FB PAGE都有大量假ACC 7*24 支持警暴<br />\n香港警魔敢強姦同水刑, 黑懲魔敢對政治犯行私刑就係因為有呢班五毛唆使<br />\n呢班低學歷賤種見到五毛的吹捧就覺得自己係主流, 覺得做任何反人類行為都得到支持<br />\n<br />\n<ins>五毛量係多到一定涉及一個好誇張的銀碼</ins><br />\n中共過去一定會叫商界DUP心口,而呢個係香港商界討好主子的好機會<br />\n故親政府地產財團100%有份"},{"pid":"185efec5fb5384ac062bdfe332a98af3f681cb09","tid":2003121,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港獨之父寄語港人：香港再出發＝抗爭再出發；並贈港人新歌曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2003117/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2003117/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n可惜，港獨之父冇咩音樂感，<br />\n原版實在太難聽，為免傷害聽力<br />\n<strong>有冇人可以幫港獨之父，重新填詞？</strong>"},{"pid":"db62ccd332b37089896a6d7f2e0748059ae503c8","tid":2003121,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:52:27.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線-烽煙節目<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2003032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2003032</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"782854327fc1c64cf58650de523a3870e409c614","tid":2003121,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0d7ab30e562bd9d617c8d91c72070da6f3184c","tid":2003121,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTi